{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "Comgini API v1 — Complete",
		"description": "Single consolidated collection for **Comgini Backend** (`/api/v1`).\n\n**Server DB (503 errors):** On the machine where MySQL runs, apply migrations once:\n`mysql -u USER -p DATABASE < src/database/deploy_secretarial_migrations.sql`\nAlso ensure `secretarial_module_tables.sql` was applied if you use secretarial search/CSR tables.\nApply `src/database/payments_module.sql` and `src/database/time_cards_module.sql` for Finance payments and HR time cards.\n\n**Includes:** Auth & profile · Dashboard & updates · Secretarial · DIR-3 / MCA V2/V3 · Shareholders · Debenture holders · Forms, DIR-2 · LLP & Company MCA · Bulk WhatsApp/Gmail · Annual filing · Documents · Directors · **Section 12:** Leads, Finance, Business, Timesheets, Time cards.\n\n**Setup:** Set `baseUrl`. Run **0. Auth → Login** to save `token`. **POST director** accepts `appointmentDate` as `YYYY-MM-DD` or `dd/mm/yyyy`. **POST bulk/whatsapp/upload** requires a real file in form field `file`.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "0. Auth",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login (saves token)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"const j = pm.response.json();",
									"const t = j.data && (j.data.accessToken || j.data.token);",
									"if (t) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', t); pm.test('Token saved', () => pm.expect(t).to.be.a('string')); }",
									"else { pm.test('Login returned token', () => pm.expect(t).to.be.ok); }"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "noauth" },
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"YourPassword123!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Get profile",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/profile"
					}
				}
			]
		},
